---
/** Modal de importación de CV desde texto o PDF (hidrata `cv-page.ts`). Mapa manual por defecto. */
---

<div
  data-cv-import-modal
  class="fixed inset-0 z-[1001] hidden items-center justify-center p-2 sm:p-3 bg-black/45 backdrop-blur-sm print:hidden"
  role="dialog"
  aria-modal="true"
  aria-labelledby="cv-import-modal-title"
>
  <div
    data-cv-import-modal-panel
    class="flex h-[min(94svh,58rem)] w-full max-w-[min(88rem,98vw)] flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 shadow-xl"
  >
    <div class="shrink-0 border-b border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 px-4 py-3 flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-2">
      <div class="min-w-0">
        <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.importModalKicker">
          Importar
        </p>
        <h2 id="cv-import-modal-title" class="m-0 text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="cv.importModalTitle">
          Texto o PDF
        </h2>
        <p class="m-0 mt-1 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.importModalIntroManual">
          Mapea el CV por colores: selecciona en el texto resaltado y asigna cada parte al formulario. Puedes pegar (Ctrl+V) o importar un PDF.
        </p>
      </div>
      <button
        type="button"
        data-cv-import-modal-close
        class="shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900"
        data-i18n="cv.importModalClose"
      >
        Cerrar
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="flex min-h-0 flex-1 flex-col gap-2 px-3 py-3 sm:px-4">
      <div class="flex shrink-0 flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
        <input type="file" accept="application/pdf,.pdf" class="sr-only" data-cv-import-modal-pdf-input tabindex="-1" />
        <button
          type="button"
          data-cv-import-modal-pdf-open
          class="rounded-lg border border-violet-300/90 dark:border-violet-700/80 bg-violet-50 dark:bg-violet-950/40 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-violet-900 dark:text-violet-100 hover:bg-violet-100 dark:hover:bg-violet-950/70"
          data-i18n="cv.importModalPdfBtn"
        >
          Elegir PDF
        </button>
      </div>

      <p class="m-0 shrink-0 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.importManualHint">
        Al entrar aquí intentamos autodetectar enlaces, email y bloques. Selecciona texto en el área de colores para asignar; el panel aparece junto a la selección.
      </p>
      <p
        class="m-0 shrink-0 text-xs text-amber-900/90 dark:text-amber-100/90 rounded-lg border border-amber-200/80 dark:border-amber-900/50 bg-amber-50/90 dark:bg-amber-950/35 px-3 py-2"
        data-i18n="cv.importReviewNote"
      >
        Revisa siempre los datos importados.
      </p>

      <textarea
        data-cv-import-paste
        class="sr-only"
        tabindex="-1"
        aria-hidden="true"
        rows="1"
        cols="1"
      ></textarea>

      <select data-cv-import-manual-target class="sr-only" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true"></select>

      <div data-cv-import-panel-manual class="flex min-h-0 flex-1 flex-col gap-3">
        <div class="flex min-h-0 flex-1 flex-col gap-2 lg:flex-row lg:items-stretch lg:gap-4">
          <div class="flex min-h-0 min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col gap-2">
            <p class="m-0 text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.importManualPreviewKicker">
              Vista con colores
            </p>
            <div
              data-cv-import-manual-surface
              tabindex="0"
              class="min-h-[16rem] flex-1 overflow-auto rounded-lg border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-50/80 dark:bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-mono leading-relaxed text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 whitespace-pre-wrap wrap-break-word outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-indigo-500/50 cursor-text select-text"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[10px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" aria-hidden="true">
              <span><mark class="bg-violet-400/42 dark:bg-violet-500/34 rounded-sm px-0.5">Titular</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-amber-400/42 dark:bg-amber-500/34 rounded-sm px-0.5">Resumen</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-sky-400/42 dark:bg-sky-500/34 rounded-sm px-0.5">Email</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-cyan-400/42 dark:bg-cyan-500/34 rounded-sm px-0.5">Teléfono</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-emerald-400/40 dark:bg-emerald-500/32 rounded-sm px-0.5">Enlace</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-rose-400/48 dark:bg-rose-500/34 rounded-sm px-0.5">Educación</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-lime-400/42 dark:bg-lime-500/32 rounded-sm px-0.5">Certif.</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-fuchsia-400/42 dark:bg-fuchsia-500/32 rounded-sm px-0.5">Idioma</mark></span>
            </div>
            <p class="m-0 text-[10px] leading-snug text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500" data-i18n="cv.importManualLegendExpHint">
              Experiencia: rol · empresa · ubic. · inicio · fin · bullets (aros: fila del formulario vs nueva fila).
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 text-[9px] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500" aria-hidden="true">
              <span><mark class="bg-indigo-400/48 dark:bg-indigo-400/32 ring-1 ring-inset ring-slate-400/35 dark:ring-slate-500/35 rounded-sm px-0.5">Rol</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-blue-400/45 dark:bg-blue-500/32 ring-1 ring-inset ring-slate-400/35 dark:ring-slate-500/35 rounded-sm px-0.5">Empresa</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-sky-400/42 dark:bg-sky-500/30 ring-1 ring-inset ring-slate-400/35 dark:ring-slate-500/35 rounded-sm px-0.5">Ubic.</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-amber-400/50 dark:bg-amber-500/36 ring-1 ring-inset ring-slate-400/35 dark:ring-slate-500/35 rounded-sm px-0.5">Inicio</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-orange-400/45 dark:bg-orange-500/34 ring-1 ring-inset ring-slate-400/35 dark:ring-slate-500/35 rounded-sm px-0.5">Fin</mark></span>
              <span><mark class="bg-lime-400/42 dark:bg-lime-500/30 ring-1 ring-inset ring-fuchsia-400/55 dark:ring-fuchsia-500/45 rounded-sm px-0.5">Bullets (nueva)</mark></span>
            </div>
            <label class="flex cursor-pointer items-start gap-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-50/60 dark:bg-gray-900/40 px-2 py-1.5">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                data-cv-import-manual-popover-follow-drag
                class="mt-0.5 h-3.5 w-3.5 shrink-0 rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600"
              />
              <span class="text-[11px] leading-snug text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300" data-i18n="cv.importManualPopoverFollowDragLabel">
                Mostrar panel de asignación mientras arrastras (atraviesa el ratón; por defecto el panel solo aparece al soltar).
              </span>
            </label>
          </div>

          <aside
            class="flex max-h-[min(40vh,18rem)] w-full shrink-0 flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-gray-200/85 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-50/50 dark:bg-gray-900/35 lg:max-h-none lg:min-h-0 lg:w-[min(24rem,32vw)] lg:max-w-[26rem]"
          >
            <div class="flex shrink-0 items-center justify-between gap-2 border-b border-gray-200/70 dark:border-gray-800 px-2 py-1.5">
              <p
                class="m-0 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                data-i18n="cv.importManualSidebarTitle"
              >
                Asignaciones
              </p>
              <button
                type="button"
                data-cv-import-manual-clear
                class="shrink-0 rounded-md border border-rose-200/90 dark:border-rose-900/50 px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-semibold text-rose-800 dark:text-rose-200 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/40"
                data-i18n="cv.importManualClearCompactBtn"
              >
                Borrar todo
              </button>
            </div>
            <div
              data-cv-import-manual-list
              class="min-h-0 flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-2 py-2 text-[11px] text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
            >
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>

        <button
          type="button"
          data-cv-import-manual-apply
          class="w-full shrink-0 rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-3 py-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-indigo-500 dark:hover:bg-indigo-500 sm:w-auto"
          data-i18n="cv.importManualApplyBtn"
        >
          Aplicar mapeo al formulario
        </button>
      </div>

      <details class="shrink-0 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-50/50 dark:bg-gray-900/30 px-3 py-2" data-cv-import-auto-details>
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 select-none" data-i18n="cv.importAutoDetailsSummary">
          Importación automática (heurística, menos fiable)
        </summary>
        <p class="m-0 mt-2 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.importPasteHint">
          Separa cada puesto o titulación con una línea en blanco…
        </p>
        <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <button
            type="button"
            data-cv-import-manual-suggest
            class="rounded-lg border border-teal-300/80 dark:border-teal-800/80 bg-teal-50/90 dark:bg-teal-950/40 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-teal-900 dark:text-teal-100 hover:bg-teal-100 dark:hover:bg-teal-950/70"
            data-i18n="cv.importManualSuggestBtn"
          >
            Autodetectar
          </button>
        </div>
        <div data-cv-import-auto-actions class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-2">
          <button
            type="button"
            data-cv-import-apply-form
            class="rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-indigo-500 dark:hover:bg-indigo-500 dark:hover:bg-indigo-400"
            data-i18n="cv.importApplyFormBtn"
          >
            Importar al formulario
          </button>
          <button
            type="button"
            data-cv-import-both
            class="rounded-lg border border-indigo-200 dark:border-indigo-800 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-indigo-900 dark:text-indigo-100 hover:bg-indigo-50 dark:hover:bg-indigo-950/50"
            data-i18n="cv.importBothBtnShort"
          >
            Solo experiencia + educación
          </button>
          <button
            type="button"
            data-cv-import-experience
            class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900"
            data-i18n="cv.importExperienceBtn"
          >
            Solo experiencia
          </button>
          <button
            type="button"
            data-cv-import-education
            class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900"
            data-i18n="cv.importEducationBtn"
          >
            Solo educación
          </button>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    data-cv-import-manual-popover
    class="hidden fixed z-[1102] w-[min(52rem,calc(100vw-0.5rem))] max-h-[min(92vh,44rem)] flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 shadow-2xl"
    role="dialog"
    aria-label="Asignar selección"
  >
    <div class="shrink-0 border-b border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 px-3 py-2">
      <p class="m-0 text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.importManualPopoverKicker">
        Asignar selección
      </p>
      <p class="m-0 mt-0.5 text-[10px] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500" data-i18n="cv.importManualPopoverHint">
        Ajusta el texto si hace falta; busca el campo y pulsa la fila para asignar (sustituye la asignación anterior del mismo campo).
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="min-h-0 flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-3 py-2 space-y-2">
      <label class="block space-y-1">
        <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.importManualPopoverBodyLabel">
          Texto que se guardará
        </span>
        <textarea
          data-cv-import-manual-popover-body
          rows="6"
          class="w-full resize-y rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-gray-50/90 dark:bg-gray-900/60 px-2 py-1.5 text-xs text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
        ></textarea>
      </label>
      <div data-cv-import-manual-popover-shortcuts class="flex flex-wrap gap-1"></div>
      <label class="block space-y-1">
        <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.importManualPopoverSearchLabel">
          Buscar destino
        </span>
        <input
          type="search"
          data-cv-import-manual-popover-filter
          class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 px-2 py-1.5 text-xs text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
          placeholder=""
          data-i18n-placeholder="cv.importManualPopoverSearchPh"
        />
      </label>
      <div
        data-cv-import-manual-popover-options
        class="max-h-[min(52vh,24rem)] overflow-y-auto rounded-lg border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-50/40 dark:bg-gray-900/30 p-2 text-xs"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
